OL,3,CSouth East Water ends hosepipe ban
OL,4,Cafter six months
OL,6,FHosepipe restrictions for South East
OL,7,FWater customers in parts of Kent and
OL,8,FSussex have been lifted, ending a
OL,9,FTemporary Use Ban that had been in
OL,10,Fplace since July.
OL,12,FThe ban, introduced on 18 July 2025,
OL,13,Faffected around 1.4 million customers
OL,14,Fafter the driest Spring in England
OL,15,Fsince 1893 led to record demand for
OL,16,Fwater.
OL,18,FThe water firm said a combination of
OL,19,Fcustomer cooperation and heavy
OL,20,Frainfall over the past two months has
OL,21,Fallowed water supplies to recover.
