OL,3,CSouth East Water ends hosepipe ban
OL,4,Cafter six months
OL,6,FRainfall so far this Winter has been
OL,7,Fabove the long-term average, helping
OL,8,FArdingly Reservoir return to full
OL,9,Fcapacity and Arlington Reservoir
OL,10,Frecover to 83%. Groundwater levels
OL,11,Fhave also improved as saturated soil
OL,12,Fhas allowed aquifers to recharge.
OL,14,FLast month, as Ardingly reservoir
OL,15,Fbegan to fill up, the Environment
OL,16,FAgency moved the area out of 'drought'
OL,17,Fand into 'recovery' status.
