OL,3,CSouth East Water ends hosepipe ban
OL,4,Cafter six months
OL,6,FNick Price, Head of Water Resources
OL,7,Ffor South East Water, wanted to thank
OL,8,Feveryone for cutting down their water
OL,9,Fuse, saying they "appreciate that
OL,10,Frestrictions impact the way people use
OL,11,Fwater and carry out daily tasks."
OL,13,FPrice wanted to remind people to
OL,14,Fcontinue being "mindful" about water
OL,15,Fuse, especially across Spring and
OL,16,FSummer this year.
